eria', 'Engage', 'Savlon' and 'Shower to Shower' covering the range of personal care products of soaps, face washes, shower gels, skin care, deodorants, handwash and ayurvedic talc, and the continuing significant brand building costs of the Foods businesses are reflected under 'Other expenses' stated above and in Segment Results under 'FMCG-Others'.  n  n4. ITC Global Holdings Pte. Limited, Singapore, ceased to be a subsidiary of the Company pursuant to its dissolution by High Court of the Republic of Singapore vide order dated 10th July, 2018.  n  n5. During the quarter ended 30th June, 2018, 31,17,410 Ordinary Shares of Re. 1/- each were issued and allotted under the Company’s Employee Stock Option Schemes (ESOS). Consequently, the issued and paid-up Share Capital of the Company as on 30th June, 2018 stands increased to Rs. 1220,74,12,321.  n  n6. This statement is as per Regulation 33 of the SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations, 2015.  n</in-bse-fin:DisclosureOfNotesOnFinancialResultsExplanatoryTextBlock>
